%8C%96/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/arch/%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/</guid><description>在 Arch Linux 上安装 Niri 滚动平铺窗口管理器与 Noctalia 桌面环境的完整流程，含字体、显示配置、输入法等</description></item><item><title>安装桌面环境前的准备</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/arch/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/arch/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87/</guid><description>在 Arch Linux 安装桌面环境前的基础配置，包含用户创建、软件源、AUR、字体、驱动、音视频服务等</description></item><item><title>软件相关</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/arch/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/arch/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/</guid><description>Arch Linux 软件安装方式汇总、推荐软件列表、AppImage 使用指南及星火应用商店配置</description></item><item><title>install niri dms</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/install-niri-dms/</link><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/install-niri-dms/</guid><description>Niri 是一个基于 Wayland 的滚动平铺窗口管理器，核心特点是横向无限卷轴式布局。不像传统桌面那样窗口只能在一个屏幕范围内排列，Niri 的工作区可以向左右无限延伸。</description></item><item><title>vscode终端黑快字体解决方案</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/vscode%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF%E9%BB%91%E5%BF%AB%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</link><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/vscode%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF%E9%BB%91%E5%BF%AB%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</guid><description>下面用清晰、结构化、可复现问题定位思路帮你总结：</description></item><item><title>配置arch</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEarch/</link><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEarch/</guid><description>A段（基础配置） ────── 装完系统后立刻做</description></item><item><title>arch linux timeshift 完整教程</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/arch-linux-timeshift-%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</link><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/arch-linux-timeshift-%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</guid><description>Timeshift 是 Linux 下最流行的系统快照工具之一。</description></item><item><title>arch zsh安装和美化指南</title><link>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/arch-zsh%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://heihei0299.github.io/posts/linux/arch-zsh%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>这份文档基于当前机器上的 ~/.zshrc 与 ~/.zshaliases 整理，目标是从零安装并复现一套兼顾颜值和效率的 zsh 环境。</description></item></channel></rss>